nodes.text: This clone trooper pilot flew one of three Plo's Bros gunships sent to Vanqor during the Clone Wars to rescue Jedi Master Mace Windu and Jedi Knight Anakin Skywalker.

Around 21 BBY, following a distress message delivered by R2-D2 to the Jedi Temple on Coruscant, Jedi Master Plo Koon and Padawan Ahsoka Tano departed to rescue fellow Jedi, Anakin Skywalker and Mace Windu, who were injured and trapped on Vanqor. This clone pilot flew the LAAT/i carrying General Koon, Commander Tano and members of the Wolfpack to aid in extracting their comrades from the crashed Venator-class Star Destroyer Endurance.
